{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Quick gameplay, easy to pick up</h2>Each battle takes only about 10 minutes, allowing you to enjoy intense and thrilling fights anytime, anywhere. Simple controls make it easy to pick up and enjoy endless exhilarating moments.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/1.gif?t=1736126775\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/2.gif?t=1736126775\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Diverse hero selection</h2>The game offers a wide range of heroes with various abilities to choose from, each providing a unique gaming experience. Find the character that suits you best and experience different combat styles.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/3.gif?t=1736126775\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unique weapon system</h2>Any weapon can fire any bullet, with different weapons having different ammo capacity, firing speed, and barrel count. Each bullet type has its unique flight trajectory, damage, and attack effects. Thousands of combinations let you create personalized weapons.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/4.gif?t=1736126775\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Strategic card building</h2>The card system in the game allows you to strengthen your abilities, and different card strategies will bring various gaming experiences. Focus on bullet penetration, area damage, or build a drone army? Explore to your heart's content!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/5.gif?t=1736126775\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Diverse level challenges</h2>Each level features different map mechanics and enemies, with unique abilities for each enemy. Challenge yourself with 20 progressively difficult levels, each adding a difficulty option to keep things fresh.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/6.gif?t=1736126775\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/7.gif?t=1736126775\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/8.gif?t=1736126775\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Rich collection elements</h2>Collect gacha coins to unlock new heroes, weapons, bullets, and cards. As the game progresses, the content will continue to grow, bringing you even more fun.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2220480/extras/9.gif?t=1736126775\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Tips for clearing levels</h2>1.Always check the store to buy and upgrade cards to strengthen yourself.<br><br>2.Lock the store when you see a suitable card to avoid the minute refresh replacement.<br>3.Prioritize upgrading the store when not under pressure to purchase more powerful cards.<br>4.Plan your card composition in advance, as there is an 8-card limit for your deck.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Grass","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2220480/785ce2d613333edbb95710e00e004b0a7534122e.jpg"},{"name":"Boneyard","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2220480/838a77af2007a47398753e08f0032b49317ce716.jpg"},{"name":"New Challenger","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2220480/9bec354369b1dd3c4b7196279b842faec7d39d98.jpg"},{"name":"Demon Sword","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2220480/f05571d58e44d33411943ed9750804f8017886a0.jpg"},{"name":"Skynet","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2220480/92e191825fb70e1a21f35db7e31e3bfb65898371.jpg"}